extendedInfo.description: Food Network (legally known as Television Food Network) is an American basic cable and satellite television channel that is operated as a joint venture between Scripps Networks Interactive (which owns 70% of the network) and the Tribune Company (which controls the remaining 30%). The channel airs both specials and regular episodic programs about food and cooking.The channel is seen in more than 90 million households across the United States. In addition to its headquarters in New York City, Food Network has offices in Atlanta, Los Angeles, San Francisco, Chicago, Detroit, Jersey City, Cincinnati, and Knoxville, Tennessee.Unofficial food network application. Mobile Site directs the Food Network.All rights belong to the food network channel(Logo and everything). Only prepared as a bookmark.
